uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.expr

Interface DateSQLExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SQLExpression<java.util.Date>, SQLValue<java.util.Date>, Targetted<java.util.Date>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DateDerefSQLExpression, MysqlDateConverter, PostgresqlDateConverter, TimestampDateFieldExpression

    public interface DateSQLExpression
extends SQLExpression<java.util.Date>
    A Date valued SQLExpression where the underlying representation is really a numeric value. This provides additional methods to access that numeric value. This should not be used for expressions that are natively implemented as a Date.
    Author:
    spb
